       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. PROJECT-SCHEDULER-PRESENTER.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01 TOTAL-MINUTES PIC S9(5) COMP-5 VALUE 0.
       01 SCORE-VALUE PIC S9V9(4) VALUE 0.
       01 SUMMARY-BUFFER PIC X(256).
       01 HEADLINE PIC X(32) VALUE "Draft Roadmap".
       01 DETAIL PIC X(32) VALUE "Assemble Budget".
       01 STAGE PIC X(32) VALUE "Schedule Review".
       01 DISPLAY-MINUTES PIC Z(5).
       01 DISPLAY-SCORE PIC -9.9999.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
MAIN.
       MOVE SPACE TO SUMMARY-BUFFER.
       CALL 'PROJECT-SCHEDULER-LOADER' USING TOTAL-MINUTES.
       CALL 'PROJECT-SCHEDULER-METRICS' USING BY VALUE TOTAL-MINUTES BY REFERENCE SCORE-VALUE.
       STRING "SCHEDULE SUMMARY: " DELIMITED BY SIZE
           HEADLINE DELIMITED BY SIZE
           " / " DELIMITED BY SIZE
           DETAIL DELIMITED BY SIZE
           " / " DELIMITED BY SIZE
           STAGE DELIMITED BY SIZE
           "!" DELIMITED BY SIZE
           INTO SUMMARY-BUFFER
       END-STRING.
       IF DETAIL = "Assemble Budget"
           STRING SUMMARY-BUFFER DELIMITED BY SIZE
               " READY" DELIMITED BY SIZE
               INTO SUMMARY-BUFFER
           END-STRING
       END-IF.
       DISPLAY SUMMARY-BUFFER.
       MOVE TOTAL-MINUTES TO DISPLAY-MINUTES.
       DISPLAY DISPLAY-MINUTES.
       MOVE SCORE-VALUE TO DISPLAY-SCORE.
       DISPLAY DISPLAY-SCORE.
       GOBACK.
       END PROGRAM PROJECT-SCHEDULER-PRESENTER.
